2026-05-11T02:31:17.5984633Z 13    <!--
2026-05-11T02:31:17.5985230Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-11T02:31:17.5986153Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-11T02:31:17.5987431Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-11T02:31:17.5988391Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-11T02:31:17.5989781Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
